quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  18,1,Udumo ungoluka-Mvelinqangi okunguyena owembula incwadi encekwini yakhe futhi wangakwenzi ubuzombezombe kuyo (iQur’an)
  18,2,"Eqondile, ukuze axwayise ngesijeziso esinzima esivela kuyena futhi alethe izindaba emzinandi kwabakholwayo, labo abenza izenzo ezilungileyo ukuthi okwabo ngumvuzo omuhle"
  18,3,Bayohlala khona ingunaphakade
  18,4,Nokuxwayisi labo abathi “uMvelinqangi unendodana”
  18,5,"Abanolwazi ngalokho ngisho nabobaba babo (abanolwazi) likhulu igama eliphuma emilonyeni yabo, abasho lutho ngaphandle kokuqamba amanga"
  18,6,Ngakho-ke uzozibulala ngenxa yokuphatheka kabi mayelana nezinyathelo zabo uma bengakholelwa kulenkulumo na
  18,7,Ngempela thina sakwenza lokho okusemhlabeni kwaba ngumhlobiso wawo ukuze sibavivinye ukuthi ngobani babo abanemisebenzi emihle ngokweqile
  18,8,"Ngempela thina siyokwenza ukuthi konke lokho okukuwona (umhlaba) kungatheli lutho, kube ngumhlaba owugwadule"
  18,9,Noma ucabanga ukuthi izihlali zasemgedeni nombhalo kwakungezinye zezimpawu zethu ezimangalisayo
  18,10,"Khumbula ngenkathi intsha ifuna ukuya kohlala emgedeni ngakho-ke yase ithi, “Nkosi yethu siphe umusa ovela kuwena futhi usenzele udaba lwethu lube ngoluqondileyo”"
  18,11,Ngakho-ke sazivala izindlebe zabo emgedeni iminyaka eminingi
  18,12,Sabe sesiyabavusa ukuze sibe inolwazi ukuthi ngeliphi phakathi kwawo womabili amaqembu elalikwazi kongcono ukubala isikhathi ababesihlalile